{
  "text": "For the most part, network operations systems were automated from operations that were previously performed manually by the telephone company employees. The generic network operation categories are: customer Services, service provisioning, network operations, planning & engineering, procurement. [CITATION_1] (1) Customer Service Activity",
  "correct_citation": {
